在加拿大：即将推出的专辑和巡演、城市音乐策略和亚历山大·斯图尔特的大年https://www.billboard.com/pro/canada-music-industry-news-upcoming-albums-alexander-stewart/Chris Eggertsen Sat, 06 Jan 2024 00:19:56 +0000 BusinessBusiness NewsCanadaInternationalVancouver https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=billboard_pro_post&p=1235576837 This week's most important music industry stories in Canada.<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>现在2023年已接近尾声， <a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Fchart-beat%2Fthese-60-songs-by-canadian-artists-charted-on-the-billboard-hot-100-in-2023&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=LNCnbzEvbmU6PWVuYxY5bsSGrByVs6zEYJEGpfIVELQ%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >年终排行榜</a>也已消化完毕，是时候展望未来了。 2024 年对于加拿大音乐来说已经是重要的一年。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>即将发行的加拿大专辑包括长期运行的流行朋克乐队 Sum 41 的双专辑、长期运行的摇滚乐队 Mother Mother 的新专辑，该专辑是继他们的老歌“Hayloft”在 TikTok 上大流行后推出的，还有来自知名乐队的新专辑。 The Strumbellas、Chromeo、古怪的流行艺术家 Allie X、乡村歌手 Corb Lund 等知名乐队。还有很多新晋艺术家的专辑值得关注。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>有前途的 BC 说唱歌手<a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Ffeatures%2Ffresh-sounds-canada-boslen-elisapie-more-canadian-music-of-the-week&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=9bqvM72SmQumXdEQOZDG5xV6Wp9TGO45pHLWiB2t6HA%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >Boslen 的<em>Conversations Over Evening</em>项目</a>暂定于三月举行。歌手/诗人<a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fmustafa-justin-trudeau-letter&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=mEftbTxYd30FE6Nziw3y1mGrp%2BWSg41b29KOxK5hu2M%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >穆斯塔法宣布</a>他的首张专辑将于今年发行。蒙特利尔说唱歌手卢·菲尔普斯 (Lou Phelps) 宣布了他即将发行的专辑<em>《Chélbé》</em> ，该专辑由 Kaytranada 担任执行制作。谈到这位炙手可热的蒙特利尔制作人，继合作专辑《Kaytraminé》之后，他<a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Ffeatures%2Ffresh-sounds-canada-kaytranada-mattmac-more&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=T3eg2WkWcn8XvKXETH%2BdbmLf1G5DcQfK%2FAgme42wK7o%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >以两首新的独唱歌曲结束了 2023 年</a>，这似乎预示着即将出现的新事物。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>本土嘻哈二人组 Snotty Nose Rez Kids 可能会在明年迎来重大突破。他们去年与加拿大索尼音乐公司签约，并<a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Ffresh-canadian-songs-of-the-week-snotty-nose-rez-kids-majid-jordan-mother-mother-more&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=O2jP4hkbXPpJZu%2FN08uhppbwbushbUtuLSv92chKSN4%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >宣布他们的主要唱片公司首张专辑将于今年夏天推出</a>。乔尼塔·甘地 (Jonita Gandhi) <a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fjonita-gandhi-2665794745&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=4LP71qkgW7wtgNwI4RlRs4eMedrYxHP6iFaeK6qsN0g%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >登上加拿大公告牌 (Billboard Canada) 的 Punjabi Wave 封面</a>后，她的首张 EP 将于 2 月在 91 North Records 发行。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>一些大型巡演也将于 2024 年登陆加拿大。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Diljit Dosanjh 将于四月在温哥华 BC Place 举办<a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Fconcerts%2Fdiljit-dosanjh-vancouver&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=O430vMYfXjUXeHpFGDlrDbRHkJdSYCnM89r5JIWc54E%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >印度以外最大的旁遮普音乐会</a>。令人惊讶的是，温哥华的场地是<a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Frock%2Frolling-stones-2024-north-american-hackney-diamonds-tour-dates-1235502055%2F&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=52ZhokX59eahvpWjvM01dcpiuvmCriJdBz9NwUeHAEY%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >滚石乐队<em>哈克尼钻石</em>巡演的唯一加拿大举办地。</a>除了在多伦多罗杰斯中心体育场举行的六场演出之外， <a  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fmusic%2Ftaylor-swift-vancouver&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=PsPNRi3QWrqw7AdMiB%2BYHhhyHi%2BbHkaTz%2FY4Ngwsox4%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >温哥华将是泰勒·斯威夫特破纪录的<em>Eras 巡回演唱会</em>中唯一在加拿大举行的演出</a>。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>流行朋克已经进入了体育场时代。退伍军人 Blink-182 和绿日队今年夏天都将对阵多伦多罗杰斯中心（蓝鸟队的主场）。 Green Day 还与 SZA 和 Noah Kahan 一起成为<a  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  href="https://nam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fca.billboard.com%2Fosheaga-headliners-2024&#038;data=05%7C02%7Cceggertsen%40billboard.com%7C469caf9cff2b49e980a708dc0d741a83%7Ce950f25546e44144a778a6ff4f557492%7C0%7C0%7C638400039571466023%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&#038;sdata=pKqE4n0OtErXdWWWpIhgWtsYetqYwDXGRGqggQvyWcg%3D&#038;reserved=0"  target="_blank"  >蒙特利尔最大音乐节 Osheaga 的头条新闻</a>。</p><p
